title: Ida Ou Guelloul
text: Ida Ou Guelloul is a small town and <a href="List%20of%20municipalities%2C%20communes%2C%20and%20arrondissements%20of%20Morocco">rural commune</a> in <a href="Essaouira%20Province">Essaouira Province</a> of the <a href="Marrakech-Tensift-Al%20Haouz">Marrakech-Tensift-Al Haouz</a> region of <a href="Morocco">Morocco</a>. In 2004, the commune had a total population of 6650 people living in 1053 households.
